subSubSection.paragraph:
Diagnostic features.
Body dorsal and ventral surfaces green to yellow. Mandibular plates subequal to clypeus and rounded apically. Anterolateral margins of pronotum straight. Humeral angles not developed (
Fig. 92
). Abdominal spine free, not reaching metacoxae (
Fig. 93
). Spiracles green, surrounded by a green maculae (
Fig. 94
). Body length: 10.00 to 15.00 mm.

